public class ExtendedDimacsArrayReader
extends DimacsArrayReader

Reader for the Extended Dimacs format proposed by Fahiem Bacchus and Toby Walsh in array representation (without the terminating 0). Adaptation of org.sat4j.reader.ExtendedDimacsReader.
